{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1612620282.1280255", "card_id": "Q_442811742", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2138}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 10 岁男孩因奶奶过年杀鸡而崩溃大哭，花一百万也要把鸡救活？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，安徽宿州，家里人杀鸡，一 10 岁男孩哭着称要把鸡救活。男孩姑姑称，家里养的鸡，本打算过年杀了吃，但孩子一直哭，最后他还把杀好的鸡给埋了。孩子从小就心软，每次在街上看到乞丐，都要爸爸妈妈拿钱给人家。奶奶过年杀鸡 10 岁男孩崩溃大哭 花一百万也要把鸡救活"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-4bb638ae93b90aeba55a1e5bd22078cb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2866 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/442811742"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI39CmvfzMkOcMEAMaCDYwNjgwNDE4IPf07YAGMJ0COIYmQAByCTQ0MjgxMTc0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1612620282.1287096", "card_id": "Q_443154151", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 325}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待文章《另一个拉姆》讲述的记者马金瑜远嫁藏区，长期遭受家庭暴力和凌虐一事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "家暴的土壤是什么？可以有哪些形式的法律或心理等援助？ 金瑜是一位曾在一线城市工作的媒体人，为了爱情，她远嫁到西部一个闭塞地区，生儿育女。养蜂养花，世外桃源般的生活，曾在媒体行业内传为美谈。现实是，她在这个过程中遭遇了长期的家暴凌虐，甚至，为了孩子她只能选择隐忍。如今，她逃离了危险地，并决心面对一切。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-374b782fc7bd06a464113ab797ad8e84_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1257 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/443154151"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I39CmvfzMkOcMEAMaCDYwNzU2ODA5IPye+YAGMCA4wAhAAXIJNDQzMTU0MTUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1612620282.1292186", "card_id": "Q_442259690", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 318}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待华为 2020 第四季度出货量大跌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-133da1ccdd821cb7890d13d3246c53f3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "992 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "ni